@startuml blockchain-signaling-system_bloss-core

actor "Network Admin" as Admin
participant "BloSS API" as BloSSAPI
participant "BloSS Manager" as BloSSManager
participant "Stalk Controller" as StalkController
participant "Pollen Blockchain" as PollenBlockchain
participant "Ethereum Network" as Ethereum
participant "IPFS" as IPFS
participant "InfluxDB" as InfluxDB

Admin -> BloSSAPI: Report attack
activate BloSSAPI

BloSSAPI -> BloSSManager: Process attack report
activate BloSSManager

BloSSManager -> PollenBlockchain: Create attack report
activate PollenBlockchain

PollenBlockchain -> PollenBlockchain: Encrypt report
PollenBlockchain -> IPFS: Store encrypted report
IPFS --> PollenBlockchain: Return IPFS hash

PollenBlockchain -> Ethereum: Deploy attack report contract
Ethereum --> PollenBlockchain: Return contract address

PollenBlockchain --> BloSSManager: Return report details
deactivate PollenBlockchain

BloSSManager -> InfluxDB: Store attack metadata
BloSSManager --> BloSSAPI: Confirm report stored
deactivate BloSSManager

BloSSAPI --> Admin: Attack reported successfully
deactivate BloSSAPI

Admin -> BloSSAPI: Request mitigation
activate BloSSAPI

BloSSAPI -> BloSSManager: Process mitigation request
activate BloSSManager

BloSSManager -> PollenBlockchain: Retrieve attack details
activate PollenBlockchain

PollenBlockchain -> Ethereum: Query contract
Ethereum --> PollenBlockchain: Return attack data

PollenBlockchain -> IPFS: Retrieve encrypted report
IPFS --> PollenBlockchain: Return encrypted data

PollenBlockchain -> PollenBlockchain: Decrypt report
PollenBlockchain --> BloSSManager: Return decrypted attack details
deactivate PollenBlockchain

BloSSManager -> StalkController: Apply mitigation
activate StalkController

StalkController -> StalkController: Update flow rules
StalkController --> BloSSManager: Mitigation applied
deactivate StalkController

BloSSManager --> BloSSAPI: Confirm mitigation
deactivate BloSSManager

BloSSAPI --> Admin: Mitigation successful
deactivate BloSSAPI

@enduml